description: Lists all landing zone operations from the past 90 days. Results are sorted by time, with the most recent operation first.

parameters.name: filter
parameters.description: An input filter for the ListLandingZoneOperations API that lets you select the types of landing zone operations to view. statuses (list) --- The statuses of the set of landing zone operations selected by the filter. (string) --- types (list) --- The set of landing zone operation types selected by the filter. (string) ---

nested_params.name: statuses
nested_params.description: The statuses of the set of landing zone operations selected by the filter.

nested_params.name: types
nested_params.description: The set of landing zone operation types selected by the filter.

nested_items.name: operationIdentifier
nested_items.description: The operationIdentifier of the landing zone operation.

nested_items.name: operationType
nested_items.description: The type of the landing zone operation.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of the landing zone operation.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: Retrieves the next page of results. If the string is empty, the response is the end of the results.
